WEBVTT

00:07.040 --> 00:08.840
ZHAOWEN BOOKSTORE

00:08.920 --> 00:11.640
You need at least a month to recover.

00:13.640 --> 00:14.800
I don't have a month.

00:15.400 --> 00:16.800
My guards are barely hanging on,

00:17.600 --> 00:19.640
and my mother hasn't been buried.

00:21.000 --> 00:24.440
What I need now isn't healing,

00:25.200 --> 00:26.840
but the strength to wield my blades.

00:30.440 --> 00:32.240
I figured you'd say that.

00:33.640 --> 00:35.120
I've prepared medicine for you.

00:36.000 --> 00:38.280
Take one when your strength gives out.

00:38.360 --> 00:39.800
But this method comes at a cost.

00:39.880 --> 00:42.400
It'll weaken your inner energy by 30%.

00:43.200 --> 00:44.480
The damage will linger.

00:45.480 --> 00:47.520
Even if the wounds heal,

00:48.360 --> 00:49.720
the pain will stay with you for life.

00:50.760 --> 00:52.560
-If you trust me…
-I trust you.

00:57.280 --> 00:59.520
To deal with them,
70% of my strength is more than enough.

01:09.800 --> 01:11.840
That half-finished
The Tale of the Silken Robe was about

01:11.920 --> 01:13.600
the impossibility of balancing loyalty
to one's ruler

01:13.680 --> 01:14.960
and filial piety to one's family.

01:15.720 --> 01:19.240
I've gone from an observer
to a character in the story itself.

01:21.200 --> 01:22.200
I remember

01:23.760 --> 01:26.120
the woman in the fox mask told me…

01:26.200 --> 01:29.680
If the second act really depicted
the son putting his father on trial,

01:30.760 --> 01:32.480
wouldn't that be shocking
and unconventional?

01:32.560 --> 01:35.360
You think a son
shouldn't judge his father?

01:35.880 --> 01:38.200
That familial bonds outweigh justice?

01:39.040 --> 01:42.480
What I mean is,
what's wrong with being unconventional?

01:46.320 --> 01:48.320
We're not characters in a play.

01:50.320 --> 01:53.280
Whatever happened in the past,
whether you believe it or not,

01:54.000 --> 01:55.120
whether it's true or false,

01:56.240 --> 01:57.320
none of it matters.

02:20.760 --> 02:22.000
How come?

02:23.080 --> 02:24.280
Are you

02:25.280 --> 02:26.400
really not her?

02:29.400 --> 02:32.200
My Lord, your focus should be
taking care of your current problem.

02:32.720 --> 02:35.240
Everything else can wait.

02:36.640 --> 02:38.480
I'll go prepare
a change of clothes for you.

02:43.520 --> 02:44.480
How did he escape?

02:45.280 --> 02:47.440
He was heavily injured!

02:49.040 --> 02:51.720
There was someone
on the inside helping him.

02:51.800 --> 02:53.320
They coordinated to break him out.

02:53.400 --> 02:56.920
Find him! Search the entire capital
if you have to!

02:57.000 --> 02:58.280
Yes, sir!

02:59.120 --> 03:00.120
Go! Go!

03:00.680 --> 03:03.240
Interrogate Song Mo's personal guard,
break them if you have to!

03:03.320 --> 03:06.960
I refuse to believe he could have
gotten far with injuries like that.

03:07.040 --> 03:08.120
-Yes, Master.
-Also,

03:09.160 --> 03:10.960
invite the elders from
the main and third branches,

03:11.040 --> 03:12.560
along with those old fools.

03:12.640 --> 03:14.920
-I'm calling for a clan council.
-Yes, Master.

03:15.880 --> 03:16.880
Wait.

03:19.680 --> 03:22.640
Have my trained death guards
been recalled?

03:22.720 --> 03:24.080
Everything's been arranged.

03:24.600 --> 03:25.600
Go.

03:26.680 --> 03:28.400
PURE AS ICE, FINE AS JADE

03:34.600 --> 03:36.160
So, you've made up your mind.

03:40.240 --> 03:41.240
You were right.

03:42.000 --> 03:43.480
No matter how shocking or unconventional,

03:44.120 --> 03:45.600
grudges and debts must be settled.

03:46.720 --> 03:47.840
Even if it costs my life,

03:48.360 --> 03:50.200
even if the world condemns me as unfilial,

03:51.760 --> 03:53.640
it will all be worth it

03:55.360 --> 03:57.280
if just one person believes me
and understands me.

03:58.200 --> 03:59.360
I promise you,

03:59.440 --> 04:01.640
no matter what you do out there

04:03.160 --> 04:04.640
or what others say,

04:05.160 --> 04:06.560
I'll stand by you.

04:08.000 --> 04:09.160
Hearing that from you

04:10.520 --> 04:11.760
is enough.

04:35.560 --> 04:36.480
This is…

04:43.480 --> 04:45.360
Young Lady, you're the lady
in the fox mask.

04:45.440 --> 04:47.480
Why won't you tell His Lordship?

04:49.600 --> 04:50.920
Things are still far from settled.

04:51.560 --> 04:54.360
I don't want him to be distracted.

05:04.360 --> 05:05.680
If I survive,

05:07.600 --> 05:09.200
I'll come back for you!

06:36.680 --> 06:40.240
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL BLOSSOM
BY AUTHOR ZIZI FROM QIDIAN CHINESE WEBSITE

06:45.360 --> 06:48.120
FUNERAL TRIBUTE

07:01.280 --> 07:05.000
DUKE OF YING'S RESIDENCE

08:10.760 --> 08:12.000
Where are my guards?

08:18.200 --> 08:21.160
ELDEST UNCLE OF SONG FAMILY, SONG MAO CHUN

08:23.560 --> 08:25.240
He's calling a clan council
in the middle of the night.

08:25.840 --> 08:27.720
But we've been waiting for four hours.

08:27.800 --> 08:29.080
Something must have gone wrong.

08:29.960 --> 08:31.760
What could possibly go wrong?

08:32.559 --> 08:34.520
He's been flogged over a hundred times.

08:34.600 --> 08:37.400
Anyone else would've been dead by now.

08:45.200 --> 08:46.040
Mao Chun.

08:59.680 --> 09:01.760
Our apologies.

09:01.840 --> 09:04.680
The nerve of you to commit murder
in the Duke of Ying's Residence!

09:04.760 --> 09:07.200
Lord Song has said that
there are intruders in the residence.

09:07.280 --> 09:10.080
The family must draw a clear line
between themselves and the intruders.

09:10.160 --> 09:11.760
Consider this the line.

09:11.840 --> 09:13.000
Those within the ancestral hall live;

09:13.720 --> 09:15.400
those outside it die

09:19.640 --> 09:21.040
-No!
-How dare you!

09:21.120 --> 09:24.600
This is the Duke of Ying's Residence!

09:26.480 --> 09:28.240
Why do all the dead look so unfamiliar?

09:28.320 --> 09:30.160
Could they really be intruders?

09:31.000 --> 09:33.800
You… You have no regard for the law!

09:34.560 --> 09:37.360
This is outrageous!

09:51.440 --> 09:52.840
Lu Zheng? Lu Zheng?

09:54.760 --> 09:56.080
Lu Zheng?

09:57.120 --> 09:59.680
It's me. I'm back.

10:01.800 --> 10:03.120
My Lord,

10:04.000 --> 10:05.320
I didn't talk.

10:06.160 --> 10:07.560
I…

10:07.640 --> 10:10.000
I didn't betray you.

10:13.160 --> 10:15.280
-Zheng!
-Go!

10:15.360 --> 10:17.200
Lu Ming, go!

10:17.280 --> 10:19.920
-Zheng!
-Get him off the door!

10:20.000 --> 10:21.640
Protect His Lordship.

10:22.160 --> 10:23.200
Hurry up.

10:23.280 --> 10:24.480
Zheng!

10:27.640 --> 10:29.840
We have go now! Go!

10:38.880 --> 10:39.720
You did well.

10:41.320 --> 10:42.560
You saved my life.

10:43.840 --> 10:45.120
All of you saved my life.

10:45.200 --> 10:46.840
They…

10:47.440 --> 10:49.920
They tried to force me
to press my fingerprint,

10:50.840 --> 10:51.920
so I…

10:52.000 --> 10:54.640
I bit my fingers until they were ruined.

10:56.360 --> 10:59.240
The others did the same.

10:59.320 --> 11:01.040
Not one of us gave in.

11:04.760 --> 11:07.560
Lu Zheng, hold on for me.

11:07.640 --> 11:09.720
The doctor will be here soon.

11:09.800 --> 11:13.120
Stay with me.
Lu Zheng, keep your eyes open!

11:16.080 --> 11:17.400
My Lord,

11:18.360 --> 11:19.520
where is my brother?

11:23.000 --> 11:24.680
Zheng, I'm here.

11:26.440 --> 11:27.440
Ming,

11:29.000 --> 11:31.840
keep…

11:31.920 --> 11:35.520
Keep His Lordship safe for me.

11:36.200 --> 11:37.560
I will.

11:37.640 --> 11:39.800
-Protect…
-I will.

11:40.720 --> 11:42.880
His Lordship.

11:44.160 --> 11:47.200
-Lu Zheng? Lu Zheng?
-Zheng?

11:48.400 --> 11:49.680
Lu Zheng!

11:49.760 --> 11:51.000
Zheng!

11:52.200 --> 11:54.480
Zheng!

11:59.720 --> 12:00.760
General!

12:16.760 --> 12:20.080
LOFTY MOUNTAINS, ADMIRABLE VIRTUES

12:32.880 --> 12:34.480
Your Grace, they've broken through!

12:34.560 --> 12:36.720
Shouldn't we escape?

12:37.240 --> 12:39.840
Very well, very well!

12:40.720 --> 12:43.320
He's just like his uncle Jiang Mei Sun!

12:44.440 --> 12:48.440
His Lordship has gone this far.

12:49.400 --> 12:51.520
-He might even…
-He won't dare.

12:51.600 --> 12:52.440
He can't.

12:52.960 --> 12:56.120
With Liaodong's Lizhen forces
pressing at the gates

12:56.200 --> 12:57.560
and external threats unresolved,

12:57.640 --> 12:59.520
His Majesty won't tolerate
any internal strife.

13:06.720 --> 13:08.400
Take this blade.

13:09.920 --> 13:11.040
Go summon reinforcements.

13:11.120 --> 13:12.440
-Me?
-Go!

13:15.680 --> 13:16.640
Yes, sir!

13:21.960 --> 13:23.200
You ungrateful son,

13:23.880 --> 13:26.680
I know exactly what you're after.

13:30.400 --> 13:31.400
Han.

13:31.960 --> 13:34.160
-Mo.
-I'm glad you're fine.

13:35.480 --> 13:36.800
Mo,

13:36.880 --> 13:38.320
please don't be mad at Father.

13:40.080 --> 13:41.160
I'm not mad.

13:42.440 --> 13:44.320
Those I ordered to kill
are traitorous servants.

13:45.000 --> 13:46.640
Only by restoring peace to the residence

13:47.160 --> 13:48.600
can we properly honor Mother's passing.

13:51.640 --> 13:53.560
Where is the jade pendant
Grandfather gave us?

13:57.320 --> 13:59.040
I've kept it with me at all times.

14:05.680 --> 14:07.280
I wasn't home when Mother was gravely ill.

14:07.360 --> 14:08.800
Tell me everything.

14:10.040 --> 14:11.240
Where is Nanny Xie?

14:11.840 --> 14:13.400
She served Mother for decades.

14:14.360 --> 14:15.480
Where is she now?

14:16.120 --> 14:19.800
They said she was unwell and
sent her back to her hometown,

14:20.600 --> 14:23.240
but she was killed by bandits on the way.

14:26.920 --> 14:29.920
Which doctor treated Mother
during her illness?

14:30.440 --> 14:32.000
Her Majesty visited several times.

14:32.520 --> 14:33.720
She was deeply concerned.

14:34.600 --> 14:36.560
The first doctor was
recommended by Her Majesty.

14:37.720 --> 14:39.840
Then, when Mother's condition
worsened in the fall,

14:40.520 --> 14:42.880
the Crown Prince recommended a new one.

14:48.600 --> 14:50.240
-Lu Ming.
-Yes, sir.

14:51.120 --> 14:53.040
-Guard Xixiang House.
-Yes, sir.

14:53.760 --> 14:54.600
Mo!

14:56.800 --> 14:58.120
I'm begging you,

14:59.520 --> 15:00.600
please don't hurt Father.

15:22.320 --> 15:23.400
Yi Chun!

15:24.120 --> 15:26.080
Come here! It's safe here.

15:44.680 --> 15:46.840
Father, don't you owe me an explanation?

15:58.480 --> 16:00.440
The Jiang family has been
branded traitors,

16:01.480 --> 16:02.520
and in your eyes,

16:03.440 --> 16:05.960
my uncle and I are no different.

16:06.840 --> 16:08.680
Since you've managed
to fight your way back,

16:09.360 --> 16:10.280
just say what you want.

16:16.240 --> 16:17.880
I've always seen you as my father,

16:18.480 --> 16:21.760
but did you ever once see me as your son?

16:22.360 --> 16:25.560
Words are meaningless now.

16:25.640 --> 16:27.520
The affair was a misunderstanding,

16:28.160 --> 16:29.680
the ones you killed were traitors,

16:30.400 --> 16:32.400
and your mother's dowry
and private assets are yours.

16:33.000 --> 16:34.120
Let's put everything

16:35.120 --> 16:36.200
behind us.

16:42.320 --> 16:44.240
Thank you for saying that.

16:45.320 --> 16:48.360
You've made it easier for me
to let go of the remaining love

16:49.520 --> 16:51.160
I had for you.

16:56.920 --> 16:59.400
This is the lantern I gave you to
express my love after you scolded me

17:00.240 --> 17:01.400
during my last visit home.

17:03.000 --> 17:05.000
I found it abandoned in
the storage room yesterday.

17:06.119 --> 17:09.440
The wick remains untouched,
and the paper is covered in ash.

17:10.839 --> 17:13.240
You never even looked at it.

17:14.520 --> 17:15.800
All these years,

17:17.640 --> 17:19.200
it was just my wishful thinking.

17:20.240 --> 17:22.240
I took 40 lashes for you,

17:22.839 --> 17:24.640
and you punished me with 100 floggings.

17:24.720 --> 17:27.040
I've repaid the debt of blood
and kinship you gave me.

17:27.839 --> 17:29.520
From this moment on,
our bond as father and son is severed,

17:30.800 --> 17:32.040
just like this lantern!

17:32.880 --> 17:35.720
The only reason I can stand here
and speak to you calmly

17:35.800 --> 17:38.280
is for the sake of Mother's funeral.

17:38.360 --> 17:39.760
I will serve as the chief mourner

17:40.480 --> 17:41.480
on the seventh day,

17:42.800 --> 17:44.600
and I will carry the banner

17:45.360 --> 17:46.560
on the forty-ninth day.

17:50.840 --> 17:53.200
You're seizing the right
to lead the funeral rites,

17:53.280 --> 17:55.320
isn't this just your way
of declaring to the capital

17:55.400 --> 17:57.680
that you've secured
your position as my heir?

17:57.760 --> 18:00.040
In the end, you're only
doing this for yourself!

18:03.880 --> 18:05.120
Since I joined the army,

18:05.200 --> 18:08.040
I've never relied on
this dukedom for anything.

18:08.120 --> 18:10.160
From now on, whatever I want,

18:11.200 --> 18:13.160
I'll earn with my own efforts.

18:14.280 --> 18:16.320
I'm moving to Grandfather's
former residence, Yizhi Hall.

18:17.000 --> 18:19.440
From now on, we have nothing
more to do with each other.

18:21.080 --> 18:22.360
But when it comes to Mother's funeral,

18:23.200 --> 18:26.400
you must fulfill your duties
as her husband

18:27.960 --> 18:29.840
and ensure she is sent off with dignity.

19:08.040 --> 19:09.120
Su Lan,

19:09.640 --> 19:11.640
burn the used bandages as well.

19:11.720 --> 19:12.960
Leave no trace behind.

19:13.600 --> 19:14.880
Yes, Young Lady.

19:27.520 --> 19:29.080
Prince Qing has sent an urgent message,

19:29.160 --> 19:32.280
Lizhen forces have repeatedly
violated our borders,

19:32.800 --> 19:35.320
causing great suffering
to the border residents.

19:36.080 --> 19:37.400
I believe

19:37.920 --> 19:41.440
we should send Wang Xing Yi
and the Jiliao Governor-General,

19:41.520 --> 19:43.160
to deploy an additional 30,000 troops

19:43.240 --> 19:44.240
to confront Lizhen.

19:44.840 --> 19:46.760
Without reinforcements,
the current Liaodong forces

19:46.840 --> 19:48.760
won't hold for long,

19:48.840 --> 19:51.320
and Lizhen could reach
Daitong within ten days.

19:54.200 --> 19:55.760
What is the state of the treasury?

19:55.840 --> 19:57.760
The Ministry of Works is still
constructing Yuan You Palace.

19:58.360 --> 19:59.960
The project is far from complete.

20:06.600 --> 20:09.320
Your Majesty, the Lizhen tribe
is extremely impoverished.

20:09.400 --> 20:11.480
They've repeatedly requested to open
horse markets in exchange for grain,

20:11.560 --> 20:12.400
which speaks volumes.

20:12.480 --> 20:15.640
Their current invasion is
likely a desperate attempt

20:15.720 --> 20:17.360
to plunder food and
livestock before winter.

20:17.960 --> 20:20.160
This conflict may not require combat.

20:20.760 --> 20:22.000
This is a discussion between

20:22.080 --> 20:24.960
the Grand Secretariat and
His Majesty about border defense.

20:25.560 --> 20:28.680
You're overstepping, Minister Dou.

20:29.520 --> 20:32.120
Grand Secretary Wu,
this concerns national security,

20:32.200 --> 20:33.840
I cannot remain silent.

20:34.440 --> 20:36.840
If this war can be resolved
within a month,

20:36.920 --> 20:39.000
the Ministry of Revenue can manage.

20:39.080 --> 20:41.200
But if it drags on for three months,

20:41.280 --> 20:44.600
we'll have to impose additional taxes
to fund the military.

20:45.200 --> 20:47.240
And in that case, how will the people

20:47.320 --> 20:50.040
of Su, Song, Jia, and Hu prefectures
manage their spring planting next year?

20:50.120 --> 20:52.360
Your Majesty, the horse markets
must not be reopened!

20:52.440 --> 20:55.040
I was demoted
for opposing this once before.

20:55.120 --> 20:57.040
I don't mind being demoted again.

20:57.120 --> 20:59.680
Opening the markets will only
breed corruption within the court

20:59.760 --> 21:01.520
and empower our enemies.

21:01.600 --> 21:02.760
I beseech Your Majesty
to make a wise decision.

21:02.840 --> 21:04.240
To guard the borders and
protect the nation's foundations

21:04.320 --> 21:06.040
is the sacred duty left
by the founding emperor.

21:06.120 --> 21:08.280
Our dynasty upholds integrity and honor.

21:08.360 --> 21:10.160
We oppose this to the death!

21:10.720 --> 21:12.560
We oppose this to the death!

21:15.520 --> 21:16.720
Your Majesty!

21:17.600 --> 21:18.960
Quick, bring Empress Wan's elixir!

21:19.600 --> 21:20.600
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

21:30.640 --> 21:32.800
If only Mei Sun were here.

21:36.600 --> 21:37.840
He's sent another one today?

21:37.920 --> 21:39.240
Yes, Master.

21:39.320 --> 21:41.040
Ever since Young Lady Zhao was grounded,

21:41.120 --> 21:42.560
Young Master Wu has been delivering

21:42.640 --> 21:44.720
a handwritten copy of Admonitions
for Women to the back gate every day,

21:44.800 --> 21:48.000
often including food
and newspapers as well.

21:51.240 --> 21:53.800
Such elegant brushwork,

21:54.480 --> 21:56.160
his handwriting really is beautiful.

22:01.560 --> 22:02.400
Has Shi Ying departed?

22:02.480 --> 22:05.040
He left right after dinner.

22:05.120 --> 22:06.560
He's headed to Taiyuan Prefecture
to audit the accounts.

22:06.640 --> 22:08.160
It'll take him at least two weeks.

22:09.760 --> 22:10.920
Master,

22:11.000 --> 22:13.280
about what Young Lady Zhao did last night,

22:13.360 --> 22:14.840
what should we do?

22:19.120 --> 22:21.760
Shou Gu's reckless and defiant attitude

22:21.840 --> 22:23.320
needs to be dealt with.

22:24.360 --> 22:26.200
Send a message to
the Office of State Affairs.

22:36.000 --> 22:37.720
FUNERAL TRIBUTE

22:48.520 --> 22:52.000
LONGEVITY

23:10.240 --> 23:13.000
Funeral rites are always led by
the head of the family.

23:13.080 --> 23:17.280
Why is the Duke of Ying's
eldest son taking over instead?

23:17.360 --> 23:19.200
Look at Song Mo, he's not even crying.

23:19.280 --> 23:20.400
How unfilial.

23:20.480 --> 23:21.480
Exactly.

23:22.160 --> 23:23.760
What's wrong with
the eldest son taking charge?

23:23.840 --> 23:26.040
Whether he's filial or not,
whether he cries or not,

23:26.120 --> 23:27.920
what does that have to do with you?

23:28.000 --> 23:29.840
For a noble family with hereditary rank,

23:29.920 --> 23:31.520
is this really all they can
manage for Lady Jiang?

23:31.600 --> 23:32.960
So shabby.

23:33.040 --> 23:36.200
Exactly. Lord Song is
always out gallivanting.

23:36.280 --> 23:38.960
I heard he didn't even make it
back to see his mother one last time.

23:40.280 --> 23:42.560
Have some decency, would you?

23:42.640 --> 23:43.760
Stop criticizing him.

23:44.720 --> 23:47.040
Where were you when Song Mo
was risking his life fighting pirates?

23:47.120 --> 23:49.440
I doubt any of you would make it
back to see your mothers either.

23:53.040 --> 23:54.880
I've come to join the rites.

23:57.600 --> 24:00.000
Don't worry, I'm here with you.

24:00.520 --> 24:02.360
From now on, no one
on all of East Fourth Street

24:02.440 --> 24:04.120
will dare say a single bad word about you.

24:07.480 --> 24:08.560
Thank you.

24:20.840 --> 24:23.840
DUKE OF DING'S ARMY, LU ZHENG

24:30.200 --> 24:31.200
My Lord,

24:32.160 --> 24:33.520
I will take my brother's place.

24:34.320 --> 24:35.680
From now on,

24:36.360 --> 24:37.400
I will protect you with my life,

24:39.000 --> 24:40.360
no matter the cost.

24:41.600 --> 24:44.000
Even if we know who killed Lu Zheng,

24:45.000 --> 24:49.080
yet cannot seek revenge right now,

24:50.880 --> 24:53.320
are you still willing to follow me?

24:57.320 --> 24:59.280
No matter what decisions you make,

24:59.920 --> 25:01.680
I will lead the charge for you.

25:02.360 --> 25:03.960
Please grant me this wish.

25:08.080 --> 25:09.120
Bring the wine.

25:17.080 --> 25:18.480
I, Song Yan Tang,

25:19.280 --> 25:21.000
will never forget your loyalty.

25:23.200 --> 25:24.760
Here's to all of you.

25:25.360 --> 25:26.520
May you rest in peace.

25:27.200 --> 25:29.120
May you rest in peace!

25:46.920 --> 25:50.160
My Lord!

26:00.560 --> 26:02.080
How did it go? No one noticed, right?

26:03.480 --> 26:04.480
Young Lady.

26:19.000 --> 26:20.120
Everything is settled.

26:20.200 --> 26:23.280
Song Mo personally oversaw Lady Jiang's
funeral as the chief mourner.

26:23.920 --> 26:24.760
He's secured his position as heir.

26:35.120 --> 26:36.280
Lu Zheng is gone.

26:38.680 --> 26:41.600
Lu Zheng, who was supposed
to live, has died early.

26:41.680 --> 26:43.280
Prepare for battle!

26:51.200 --> 26:52.480
Sister.

26:56.600 --> 26:58.240
-Who is it?
-Young Lady Zhao,

26:58.320 --> 27:00.520
Master Shi Shu requests
your presence at the ancestral hall.

27:15.480 --> 27:16.480
Uncle Shi Shu.

27:17.000 --> 27:18.880
May I know why you want
to see me at this hour?

27:20.320 --> 27:21.320
Shou Gu,

27:21.880 --> 27:25.240
you've always made it clear you
don't want to marry the Marquis of Jining.

27:25.840 --> 27:28.160
Why don't you just tell us the truth now?

27:28.680 --> 27:31.880
Perhaps we can still
find a way to help you.

27:31.960 --> 27:33.080
What does that mean?

27:34.520 --> 27:36.400
-Zou Er.
-Yes, Master.

27:42.960 --> 27:45.280
-I clearly burned…
-Su Lan.

27:45.360 --> 27:46.560
You clearly burned what?

27:47.480 --> 27:49.360
This bloodstained garment really
does have something to do with you.

27:49.960 --> 27:52.120
Shi Shu, this is solid evidence.

27:52.920 --> 27:54.280
Why would you assume

27:54.360 --> 27:56.360
I had something to do with
the bloodstained garment?

27:58.400 --> 28:00.960
You went behind your family
and meet a man in secret at night.

28:01.040 --> 28:02.560
You're disgracing the entire family.

28:03.280 --> 28:04.240
Guards!

28:04.760 --> 28:07.240
Young Lady Zhao has dishonored the family.

28:07.320 --> 28:08.920
Prepare the family punishment.

28:09.520 --> 28:10.520
Yes, Master.

28:15.240 --> 28:17.800
Master, the family punishment is ready.

28:17.880 --> 28:18.920
Madam Ying Xue is waiting for you.

28:21.080 --> 28:24.200
I wanted the elder daughter to
marry for status, the second for power.

28:24.280 --> 28:25.760
Everything should've gone perfectly.

28:26.960 --> 28:28.400
But this pawn refused to play its part

28:29.000 --> 28:30.720
leading to a losing move.

28:32.960 --> 28:36.480
Find a way to leak news
of Dou Zhao to Wu Shan.

28:37.160 --> 28:39.120
If we can exchange this pawn
for another advantage,

28:40.040 --> 28:42.120
it will still be worth it.

28:43.120 --> 28:44.080
ROOK

28:44.680 --> 28:46.640
What do you mean, Master?

28:48.640 --> 28:50.600
Wu Shan has always desired Dou Zhao

28:51.320 --> 28:52.800
but couldn't have her.

28:53.400 --> 28:55.120
If he learns she's suffering,

28:57.040 --> 28:58.840
won't he be desperate to save her?

29:01.280 --> 29:03.320
Understood. I'll see to it immediately.

29:25.640 --> 29:26.680
Thank His Grace!

29:26.760 --> 29:28.040
You're finally awake, My Lord!

29:28.920 --> 29:29.920
His Lordship is awake!

29:33.360 --> 29:34.360
My Lord.

29:35.280 --> 29:37.920
My Lord, you're finally awake.

29:42.080 --> 29:43.000
How long was I asleep?

29:44.640 --> 29:45.920
Seven full days.

29:47.040 --> 29:50.320
The imperial physicians
came several times.

29:51.120 --> 29:53.200
They said you'd injured
your internal organs,

29:53.280 --> 29:54.880
overstrained your body with medicine,

29:55.560 --> 29:57.000
and drained your spirit.

29:57.760 --> 29:59.160
They said you might never wake up again.

30:00.600 --> 30:03.480
Thankfully, you've made it back
from death's door.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.360
Where is Dou Zhao?

30:07.440 --> 30:08.640
How is she?

30:08.720 --> 30:10.560
-Young Lady Zhao is…
-Lu Ming.

30:14.120 --> 30:15.120
What happened?

30:15.640 --> 30:16.720
Tell me!

30:18.640 --> 30:20.240
Mr. Chen said

30:20.760 --> 30:23.120
Young Lady Zhao was punished
by Master Shi Shu

30:24.120 --> 30:25.520
for meeting a man in secret at night.

30:32.600 --> 30:33.880
Meeting a man in secret?

30:34.640 --> 30:35.640
That was me.

30:38.960 --> 30:40.960
-My Lord.
-My Lord.

30:41.920 --> 30:44.200
The chaos in your residence
has only just settled,

30:44.280 --> 30:45.800
and you've barely survived.

30:45.880 --> 30:47.920
-Your body can't take this.
-He's right.

30:51.720 --> 30:52.760
She saved my life.

30:53.280 --> 30:54.640
If my body can't take it,

30:54.720 --> 30:56.320
then consider it as returning
the favor to her.

30:56.400 --> 30:58.840
The matter regarding Young Lady Zhao
has settled down.

30:59.560 --> 31:00.880
But the Wu family…

31:02.880 --> 31:03.880
The Wu family?

31:04.400 --> 31:05.680
What about the Wu family?

31:09.240 --> 31:10.640
-Young Master, you can't go in!
-Go away!

31:10.720 --> 31:12.520
-You can't go in!
-Get out of my way!

31:12.600 --> 31:14.760
What are you doing to her?
Are you trying to kill her?

31:14.840 --> 31:15.960
Get away from her!

31:17.280 --> 31:18.320
Young Lady Zhao.

31:29.240 --> 31:30.440
The bloodstained garment is mine.

31:31.480 --> 31:33.920
Young Master Wu, you cannot
say such things recklessly!

31:34.000 --> 31:35.760
How could that garment
possibly belong to you?

31:35.840 --> 31:38.000
I coughed up blood due to my lung ailment.

31:38.080 --> 31:39.640
Well, well, the Wu family heir
lives up to his reputation.

31:39.720 --> 31:40.800
How responsible.

31:42.040 --> 31:43.120
But isn't that excuse

31:44.040 --> 31:45.520
a little far-fetched?

31:45.600 --> 31:47.160
I was the one who acted rashly

31:48.240 --> 31:49.960
and behaved inappropriately.

31:50.040 --> 31:51.840
Young Lady Zhao is completely blameless.

31:52.360 --> 31:55.560
Please punish me instead, Minister Dou.

31:56.160 --> 31:58.280
Grand Sectary Wu abuses his influence,

31:58.360 --> 32:00.880
allowing his grandson to
trespass on private residences

32:00.960 --> 32:02.960
and seduces a betrothed daughter
of our family,

32:03.480 --> 32:05.280
treating our family with utter disrespect.

32:05.360 --> 32:07.200
This is beyond my authority.

32:07.880 --> 32:09.960
I'll hand you over
to the Office of State Affairs.

32:15.480 --> 32:17.400
Seducing the legitimate daughter
of a noble family

32:18.360 --> 32:20.760
is a crime punishable by death.

32:21.960 --> 32:23.400
What a pity.

32:24.840 --> 32:25.960
That night,

32:26.640 --> 32:28.400
I was seeking medical advice.

32:30.360 --> 32:32.160
There was nothing improper between us.

32:32.240 --> 32:34.320
You're the son of a noble family,

32:34.400 --> 32:36.680
yet you've been visiting
Dou's Residence frequently.

32:36.760 --> 32:38.040
How could you claim innocence?

32:38.800 --> 32:40.400
Or perhaps there's more to it.

32:40.480 --> 32:44.200
Grand Sectary Wu has been lobbying
for war against Lizhen.

32:44.280 --> 32:47.600
Were you at their residence
to gauge their stance

32:47.680 --> 32:49.280
and push your grandfather's agenda?

32:50.760 --> 32:53.520
What does this have to do
with my grandfather?

32:54.600 --> 32:56.480
In times of crisis,
loyal ministers reveal their character.

32:57.000 --> 32:58.480
In chaos, true patriots stand out.

32:59.320 --> 33:00.720
Defending the nation with one's life

33:01.640 --> 33:03.480
is the duty of every subject.

33:04.440 --> 33:06.440
There's no room for tolerating treachery.

33:07.040 --> 33:09.760
Why would that require lobbying?

33:11.600 --> 33:13.080
So, Wu Shan claims

33:13.840 --> 33:17.600
Grand Secretary Wu believes
we live in dangerous, chaotic times,

33:17.680 --> 33:19.800
that those advocating for peace
are disloyal,

33:19.880 --> 33:22.600
and that His Majesty
is harboring traitors.

33:23.200 --> 33:26.360
Wu Shan admits to using
the Dou family's daughter

33:26.440 --> 33:28.440
to probe the officials' stance,

33:28.520 --> 33:31.480
intending to form factions.

33:31.560 --> 33:32.560
That's not true.

33:33.840 --> 33:35.360
You're twisting my words!

33:35.440 --> 33:36.800
Who are you people?

33:38.000 --> 33:39.080
Guards!

33:39.720 --> 33:41.960
I demand to see Dou Shi Shu!

33:42.640 --> 33:44.200
Buckets of bloody water were poured out

33:44.280 --> 33:46.240
from the prison of
the Office of State Affairs.

33:46.320 --> 33:49.160
Every confession has been steered
toward accusations of the Wu family

33:49.240 --> 33:51.040
lobbying and forming factions.

33:51.120 --> 33:54.000
What about the civil officials
who frequented our bookshop?

33:56.000 --> 33:58.000
They've returned all the money.

34:02.360 --> 34:03.600
I thought

34:05.160 --> 34:06.800
I saved his life,

34:08.480 --> 34:09.760
but now it seems

34:11.800 --> 34:13.480
I owe him mine.

34:19.719 --> 34:22.400
De Zhen has always been on good terms
with your family.

34:22.480 --> 34:27.320
You know his character well.

34:28.560 --> 34:30.760
Please show him mercy.

34:32.639 --> 34:35.440
I know the importance of separating
personal feelings from official matters.

34:35.960 --> 34:37.400
You can put your mind at ease, Xing Yi,

34:37.480 --> 34:39.639
and please assure
Grand Secretary Wu as well,

34:39.719 --> 34:40.719
it's not a serious matter.

34:43.320 --> 34:46.600
Grand Secretary Wu and I
will never forgot this favor.

34:46.679 --> 34:48.719
On behalf of my foolish student…

34:49.440 --> 34:50.480
Thank you.

34:51.840 --> 34:52.880
It's nothing.

34:55.080 --> 34:56.080
Goodbye.

35:11.240 --> 35:12.440
Uncle Shi Shu,

35:13.200 --> 35:16.360
I beg you, please spare Wu Shan
and the Wu family.

35:17.560 --> 35:19.000
Go back, Zhao.

35:19.080 --> 35:20.360
This is no longer your concern.

35:20.440 --> 35:22.840
Ever since Wu Shan was sent to prison,

35:23.760 --> 35:28.200
the servants of officials, big and
small, have been swarming our residence.

35:29.080 --> 35:30.920
Even Minister Mu and
Minister Zhao have come in person.

35:31.520 --> 35:33.840
Every day, countless secret letters
pour in like a flood.

35:34.360 --> 35:35.800
It's clear this isn't something
they intend to let slide

35:37.600 --> 35:39.640
Women being too clever
is never a good thing.

35:39.720 --> 35:41.440
For most families,

35:41.520 --> 35:42.960
a scandal like this is just
a private disgrace.

35:43.840 --> 35:45.000
But the Wu family

35:45.080 --> 35:48.200
has held power for decades.

35:49.200 --> 35:51.400
It's time for them to step aside
and make room for others.

35:52.280 --> 35:54.240
The fall of the century-strong Wu family

35:57.080 --> 35:58.920
would pave the way for your ambitions

35:59.800 --> 36:00.880
and make your name shine in history.

36:01.480 --> 36:04.280
This was your plan all along, wasn't it?

36:04.360 --> 36:06.440
A wise man waits for the right moment

36:06.520 --> 36:07.520
and acts in accordance with the times.

36:08.400 --> 36:10.200
Going against the tide

36:10.280 --> 36:12.280
will never end well.

36:13.200 --> 36:14.200
Uncle.

36:18.640 --> 36:20.960
I'm begging you.

36:21.560 --> 36:23.400
Please spare Wu Shan!

36:32.320 --> 36:34.760
ORCHID AND ANGELICA FOREVER FLOURISHING

36:38.080 --> 36:39.000
Young Lady,

36:39.640 --> 36:41.360
Mr. Chen has sent word.

36:41.440 --> 36:42.400
Lord Song has woken up.

36:45.040 --> 36:46.320
That's good.

36:47.480 --> 36:50.320
Mr. Chen said His Lordship

36:50.400 --> 36:52.040
has learned about
the bloodstained garment.

36:52.680 --> 36:54.920
He's going to the Office of State
Affairs to clear Young Master Wu's name.

36:55.000 --> 36:56.360
He mustn't!

36:57.400 --> 36:58.720
If he goes now,

36:58.800 --> 37:00.240
he'll end up dead alongside Wu Shan.

37:00.840 --> 37:02.600
Whether it's Uncle Shi Shu, Song Yi Chun,

37:03.200 --> 37:05.240
or the mastermind behind
the Duke of Ding's death,

37:05.320 --> 37:06.680
they're all hoping for that outcome.

37:07.360 --> 37:09.160
Even Yan Chao Qing co
culdn't dissuade him,

37:09.240 --> 37:10.160
And you're still grounded.

37:14.320 --> 37:15.360
Shou Gu!

37:44.840 --> 37:45.840
Shou Gu,

37:46.800 --> 37:48.000
I came back too late.

37:48.720 --> 37:51.400
So much happened
while I was away in Chanxi.

37:51.920 --> 37:53.320
I know you've been wronged.

37:53.920 --> 37:55.800
How are your injuries?
Let me take a look at you.

37:56.560 --> 37:58.400
It was all for our family's future.

37:59.720 --> 38:02.160
My injuries don't matter.

38:03.600 --> 38:04.560
Shou Gu,

38:05.560 --> 38:07.520
I only just learned about this.

38:08.120 --> 38:09.080
If I had been home,

38:09.160 --> 38:11.120
I would never have let them hurt you.

38:11.880 --> 38:14.120
Young Master Wu is suffering
far worse injuries in prison.

38:14.200 --> 38:16.040
You've always valued him highly.

38:16.560 --> 38:17.840
Why haven't you gone to see him?

38:23.280 --> 38:24.520
After over ten years,

38:26.360 --> 38:27.880
I've returned to your side again,

38:29.320 --> 38:31.160
and what have I received?

38:32.200 --> 38:35.240
Slaps, punishments and nothing else.

38:39.160 --> 38:40.160
Father,

38:42.240 --> 38:43.560
is my house arrest

38:45.000 --> 38:47.240
going to last forever?

38:48.280 --> 38:49.240
Of course not.

38:50.080 --> 38:51.480
It's lifted,

38:51.560 --> 38:54.320
immediately, right now!

38:58.320 --> 39:01.760
My Lord, turning yourself in now
will undo everything we've worked for.

39:01.840 --> 39:03.320
De Zhen is too naive and frail

39:03.400 --> 39:05.520
to endure the coercion and torture
of the Office of State Affairs.

39:06.040 --> 39:07.520
I can't let him take the blame for me.

39:07.600 --> 39:09.680
Even if I turn myself in,
I have a way to get out.

39:43.040 --> 39:45.320
What are you doing out here
in this wind and storm?

39:45.400 --> 39:48.240
Your feet are injured.
are you trying to make it worse?

39:48.760 --> 39:50.040
You made me a promise,

39:51.480 --> 39:52.400
that if I saved you,

39:53.360 --> 39:54.840
you'd cherish your life

39:54.920 --> 39:55.760
and fight for a way forward.

39:57.040 --> 39:58.040
Right now,

39:58.120 --> 40:00.160
you're in no position to save Wu Shan.

40:00.680 --> 40:03.520
You'll only give those in the shadows
more reasons to frame you,

40:04.760 --> 40:07.040
bringing pain to those who care for you
and joy to your enemies

40:23.280 --> 40:24.320
I can do it myself.

40:24.400 --> 40:26.480
Stay still, or you'll scrape your wound.

40:31.280 --> 40:32.840
Didn't you say once

40:33.600 --> 40:34.720
that in a doctor's eyes,

40:34.800 --> 40:36.120
everyone is just flesh and bone,

40:36.200 --> 40:37.400
no distinction between men and women?

40:38.200 --> 40:39.160
Why are you being shy now?

40:40.400 --> 40:42.240
Only my feet are injured,

40:42.320 --> 40:43.520
my hands are fine.

40:44.320 --> 40:46.120
Besides, they had other motives

40:46.200 --> 40:47.760
for the punishment,

40:47.840 --> 40:49.360
so they didn't really use much force.

40:49.440 --> 40:50.760
My feet will be fine.

40:52.720 --> 40:54.480
What about you? Are you all right?

40:55.000 --> 40:56.400
Let me check your pulse.

41:15.280 --> 41:16.480
How did the Wu family

41:17.600 --> 41:18.920
end up getting dragged into this?

41:20.720 --> 41:23.000
Uncle Shi Shu deliberately
leaked word of me being punished

41:23.080 --> 41:24.720
to the Wu family.

41:24.800 --> 41:26.480
He even fabricated a bloodstained garment.

41:27.920 --> 41:29.480
Wu Shan ended up in prison

41:29.560 --> 41:30.560
because he was trying to save me.

41:31.440 --> 41:33.480
I sent someone to inquire
at the Office of State Affairs.

41:33.560 --> 41:36.400
All his confessions are twisted
to accuse him of factionalism.

41:37.160 --> 41:38.800
I can't believe so much happened

41:39.320 --> 41:40.480
in just a few days when I was in a coma.

41:42.480 --> 41:44.560
But Uncle Shi Shu's words
did make me see things clearly.

41:44.640 --> 41:46.800
A wise man waits for the right moment

41:46.880 --> 41:48.480
and acts in accordance with the times.

41:48.560 --> 41:49.800
Going against the tide

41:50.720 --> 41:52.280
will never end well.

41:52.880 --> 41:56.040
This case is no longer
about whether we had a relationship.

41:56.120 --> 41:58.760
It's about whether the Lizhen
uprising in Liaodong

41:58.840 --> 42:01.560
should be met with war or peace.

42:02.960 --> 42:04.360
What's the situation in Liaodong?

42:04.960 --> 42:07.000
Grand Secretary Wu
and the Grand Secretariat ministers

42:07.080 --> 42:08.160
are resolutely advocating for war,

42:08.840 --> 42:10.520
even citing the founding emperor's edicts.

42:11.320 --> 42:13.440
But His Majesty is reluctant
to go to war with Lizhen.

42:14.160 --> 42:16.720
After all, the treasury is in deficit,

42:16.800 --> 42:18.240
and the nation lacks capable generals.

42:18.320 --> 42:19.560
His Majesty doesn't want war?

42:21.800 --> 42:23.480
Liaodong's forces are stretched thin

42:24.120 --> 42:25.880
and lack experience
in direct confrontation.

42:25.960 --> 42:28.680
Plus, the treasury is empty,
making a prolonged war unsustainable.

42:28.760 --> 42:30.680
Grand Secretary Wu's push for war
comes from a place of loyalty,

42:31.960 --> 42:33.520
but the more fervently he argues,

42:33.600 --> 42:35.320
the harder it is for His Majesty
to back down.

42:36.440 --> 42:38.600
For Uncle Shi Shu, who has been
laying low for so many years,

42:39.200 --> 42:41.280
to suddenly accuse
the Wu family so boldly,

42:41.880 --> 42:43.400
he must have read His Majesty's mind.

42:45.120 --> 42:46.160
Based on what you've said,

42:46.240 --> 42:48.400
Grand Secretary Wu's advice is ill-timed

42:48.480 --> 42:49.480
and bound to lead to his downfall.

42:50.840 --> 42:51.840
This case

42:52.520 --> 42:54.080
is only going to get harder to resolve.

42:58.840 --> 43:01.680
If they could set aside questions of
right and wrong, pride and disgrace,

43:01.760 --> 43:03.320
perhaps this stalemate could be broken.

43:06.600 --> 43:08.000
The key lies in resolving the tension

43:08.640 --> 43:10.720
between Grand Secretary Wu
and His Majesty.

43:27.640 --> 43:31.120
The most unpredictable thing in the world
is the human mind.

43:31.200 --> 43:33.120
Even if I could go back,

43:33.200 --> 43:35.600
I doubt I could sit back and do nothing.

43:36.200 --> 43:39.880
I would rather die than admit
to these fabricated accusations.

43:39.960 --> 43:41.240
Execute him!

45:32.080 --> 45:33.480
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
DURING THE MAKING OF THIS FILM.

45:33.560 --> 45:34.880
MEDICAL ACTS AND DRUGS IN THIS DRAMA
ARE FICTIONAL. DO NOT IMITATE.
